Conflicts: squid3 (<< ${binary:Version})
Replaces: squid3
Description: Full featured Web Proxy cache (HTTP proxy)
 Squid is a high-performance proxy caching server for web clients, supporting
 FTP, gopher, ICY and HTTP data objects.

